BENG 313: Physiology for Engineers. 3 credits.
Provides a broad introduction to the subject of human physiology, focusing on learning the subject matter from an engineering viewpoint. Emphasis on organs and physiological systems where engineering has a significant role.  Offered by Bioengineering. Limited to two attempts. Equivalent to BENG 214.
